{"tid":714924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先差啲踼到個廢老仆街","createTime":"2018-06-24T04:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T06:04:29.000Z","uid":11779,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52d7291bac6203fe04e4a3d9e666518c9d26c364","tid":714924,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"過緊馬路時個綠燈閃閃下差唔多完，咁啲人一定會行快幾啲啦，我前面有個廢老一上到行人路就急停。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我停唔切個膝頭一野批左落佢屎忽度，搞到個老野差啲仆街，佢本來想屌鳩我，但我先聲奮人，屌鳩佢做咩過完馬路就急停，塞住條路，咁對後面啲人好危險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個老野知自己理虧就冇出聲，而我就好自豪咁行走左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cb5397b7410f74c43abbbdab8c73477da87c27","tid":714924,"uid":91664,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"現實：俾廢老屌到仆街"},{"pid":"ed5e052291ac1e29b27550747a624e41d962562a","tid":714924,"uid":11779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61cb5397b7410f74c43abbbdab8c73477da87c27","tid":714924,"uid":91664,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:48:48.000Z","msg":"現實：俾廢老屌到仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dca2d10213da3746cca6ecc7942480dfe44d45","tid":714924,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"廢老心諗：「不屌了，要返工」"},{"pid":"c83c71e1a8931e2b0d48d775546d4400dad9ce3e","tid":714924,"uid":11779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0dca2d10213da3746cca6ecc7942480dfe44d45","tid":714924,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"廢老心諗：「不屌了，要返工」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T05:04:56.000Z","msg":"廢老返工？"},{"pid":"3acb9a668002824bc3e78a44a4bda083d0d6e270","tid":714924,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c83c71e1a8931e2b0d48d77554